gif" alt=":(" class="wp-smiley" /><br />\nAnyway, Also for AdRotate Free; Cookies, bugfixes and other tweaks. Because of cookies the plugin should now be faster. Let me know if you notice a speed boost. A number of functions are made more efficient and overall a lot less queries should be made to your database.</p>\n<h3>Changes</h3>\n<div class="shortcode-unorderedlist arrow">\n<ul>\n<li>[new] Cookies for Impression tracking (24h)</li>\n<li>[new] Cookies for Click tracking (24h)</li>\n<li>[tweak] Impression timer defaults to 60 seconds on new installs</li>\n<li>[tweak] Much more accurate impression counter in Dynamic Groups</li>\n<li>[tweak] Improved efficiency use of queries on stats</li>\n<li>[tweak] adrotate_ad() no longer used for groups</li>\n<li>[tweak] Faster Post Injection selection</li>\n<li>[fix] Wrapper code parsed twice on some ads</li>\n<li>[fix] Mixed mode post injection now works as intended</li>\n<li>[fix] Post injection now also works for posts with multiple categories</li>\n</ul>\n<p></div>\n<br />\n</h3>\n<img src="//feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AdrotatePluginForWordpress/~4/DiCRa5DB0PY" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:94:"https://www.adrotateplugin.com/2014/11/adrotate-free-3-10-13-cookies-speed-bump-bugfixes/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:89:"https://www.adrotateplugin.com/2014/11/adrotate-free-3-10-13-cookies-speed-bump-bugfixes/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"x